Title: Big Joe Turner sitting in a van in Long Beach, 1980 [descriptive]
Description.note: Black and white photograph of blues singer Big Joe Turner and his wife, sitting in PeeWee Crayton's van at the 1st KLON Blues Festival. Officially known as the "KLON Blues & Gospel Festival," the festival was held at Veterans Park, Long Beach. It was later renamed the Long Beach Blues Festival.
